Condo resale prices  volumes rise at a slower pace in May: SRX 99.co:Source1. CONDOMINIUM resale prices and volumes continued to rise in May  albeit at a slower pace  indicated on flash estimates from SRX and99.coreleased on Tuesday (Jun 27).2. Overall resale prices rose 0.9 per cent from April and were up 9.2 per cent year on year.3. However  not all regions registered price increases. The Core Central Region (CCR) and Outside Central Region (OCR) rose 1.7 per cent and 1.6 per cent  respectively  while prices in the Rest of Central Region (RCR) slid 0.3 per cent.More here
